    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/cdbc91017b3ccb1fe46b2e5493bccdc9.poster.avif?t=1771962061\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/cdbc91017b3ccb1fe46b2e5493bccdc9.webm?t=1771962061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/cdbc91017b3ccb1fe46b2e5493bccdc9.mp4?t=1771962061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事背景设定在末日灾难后的日本，人类仅存的希望寄托在艾玛和小库身上。艾玛因痛苦而遭受社会排斥，小库则是一条孽蚀犬。他们共同踏上一场宏大的冒险之旅，这是一款一人一狗并肩作战的动作角色扮演游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这段旅程中，你会经历孤独与失落，也会感受同伴的可靠与温暖。在这个无常多变的世界中，森林可能会突然从废土中拔地而起。随着艾玛和小库在这美丽而又严酷的世界中穿行，他们之间的羁绊以及能力也在不断成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过独特的技能树、装备和灵秘石来定制自己的游戏风格，在这美丽而严酷的世界中生存下去。根据你的喜好来选择装备，包括远程、潜行和激进的战斗方式，定义你的专属游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个孽蚀肆虐的世界中……在旅程的终点究竟会遇到什么呢？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>艾玛和小库的协同效应</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艾玛和小库共同造就了这款革命性的动作角色扮演游戏。与主角艾玛一起战斗，运用剑术能力，同时指挥小库释放各种技能，就像在回合制角色扮演游戏中一样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/6474b7057b2711f5e3a58df07b5b5432.poster.avif?t=1771962061\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/6474b7057b2711f5e3a58df07b5b5432.webm?t=1771962061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/6474b7057b2711f5e3a58df07b5b5432.mp4?t=1771962061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>日本：4026 年</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿行于美丽而严酷的后末日世界中。体验孽蚀之森中不断变化的景色，遭遇统治此地的头目。在远东相遇的艾玛和小库，肩负着与来自世界各地的头目进行战斗并夺取其力量以击败轮回之兽的使命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/e9752a805eb9e40a569710434b2b27d3.poster.avif?t=1771962061\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/e9752a805eb9e40a569710434b2b27d3.webm?t=1771962061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/e9752a805eb9e40a569710434b2b27d3.mp4?t=1771962061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>神秘莫测的故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于残酷的叙事之中，每个角色的背后都隐藏着危险的真相。在这深刻的故事中，揭示艾玛与小库交织的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/e5919f9bb97190a7efde0765fd70104f.poster.avif?t=1771962061\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/e5919f9bb97190a7efde0765fd70104f.webm?t=1771962061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001760/extras/e5919f9bb97190a7efde0765fd70104f.mp4?t=1771962061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
